responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "F36103DE4C07CD0DDA16B58A71B9F0DC", "The necklace. My beloved daughters. The Everspring. I remember, somewhat. My quest for the maidens led me to my madness and to my sundering. I must call to them, but I cannot call to them without my beloved\'s trinket of a mother\'s love. The Mother of Maiden. The necklace. ")
